      "text": "Recently started to add xrpc endpoints to my sites, so now I can do this sort of stuff without actually hitting the gallery:\n\n~~~PowerShell\nirm mrpowershell.com/xrpc/com.pow... | %{ $_ } | ? Published -gt ([datetime]::Now.AddYears(-1))  | Measure-Object\n~~~\n\nSo, yeah, 23 modules in the past year."
